messages.content:
Analyze this auction item for resale potential:
Title: {{title}}
Price: ${{currentPrice}}
Condition: {{condition}}
Description: {{description}}

Extract:
1. Brand and exact model
2. Key selling features
3. Potential issues/red flags
4. Estimated retail value
5. Resale difficulty (1-10)
6. Shipping complexity (1-10)

Format as JSON.

Create an optimized eBay listing for resale:

Item Details:
- Title: {{title}}
- Brand: {{brand}}
- Condition: {{condition}}
- Purchase Price: ${{purchasePrice}}

Generate:
1. SEO-optimized title (80 chars max)
2. Detailed description with bullet points
3. Suggested starting price: ${{multiply(purchasePrice, 1.4)}}
4. Buy It Now price: ${{multiply(purchasePrice, 1.8)}}
5. Keywords for search optimization
6. Category suggestions

Format as JSON with fields: title, description, starting_price, bin_price, keywords, category_id

Extract tracking information from this email. Return JSON with fields: tracking_number, carrier, status, expected_delivery_date

Email Subject: {{emailSubject}}
Email Content: {{emailContent}}

Generate a comprehensive daily performance report for the Automated Auction Assistant:

Daily Statistics:
- Items Won: {{itemsWon}}
- Items Sold: {{itemsSold}}
- Total Revenue: ${{totalRevenue}}
- Total Profit: ${{totalProfit}}
- ROI: {{roiPercentage}}%
- Win Rate: {{winRate}}%
- Active Listings: {{activeListings}}

Top Performing Items Today:
{{topItems}}

Include:
1. Performance summary
2. Key insights and trends
3. Recommendations for tomorrow
4. Risk assessment
5. Action items

Format as professional business report.

